10 days 10 project
08/07/2024 - 16/07/2024

1.✅Image Carousel (Create an image carousel that automatically transitions between images every few seconds and allows manual navigation.)
2.✅ Form Validation (Implement a form with input fields for name, email, and password, and validate the input on submission.)
3.✅ Tooltip Feature (Create a tooltip that appears when hovering over a text element and disappears when the mouse leaves.)
4.✅ Accordion Menu (Build an accordion menu where clicking on a section header expands or collapses the section content.)
5.✅ Drag and Drop Interface (Implement a basic drag and drop interface where users can drag items from one container to another.)
6.✅ Countdown Timer (Create a countdown timer that counts down from a specified number of seconds and displays a message when time is up.)
7.✅Simple Calculator (Build a simple calculator with basic operations (addition, subtraction, multiplication, division). Use buttons for digits and operations, and display the result.)
8.✅Sticky Header (Create a sticky header that remains at the top of the page when scrolling down.)
9.✅Dynamic List with Add/Remove Items (Create a dynamic list where users can add new items to the list and remove existing items.)
10. Interactive Quiz (Build an interactive quiz with multiple-choice questions, where selecting an answer shows whether it is correct or not.)